flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[User initiates GIF search]
    B --> C[System retrieves GIFs from database]
    C --> D[Display GIF results to user]
    D --> E[User selects a GIF]
    E --> F[System prepares GIF for sending]
    F --> G[User confirms sending GIF]
    G --> H[System sends GIF to recipient]
    H --> I[End]